          "_name": "team01",
          "_sourceTheme": "woodm4",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"team1 woodm4_team1\" group=\"Teams\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        \n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Images\" name=\"showImages\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Name\" name=\"showName\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Status\" name=\"showBio\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Phone\" name=\"showphone\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Email\" name=\"showmail\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Line Color\" name=\"line\" value=\"#b69b74\" selected>\n        <select title=\"Cards Count\" name=\"TestimonialsCount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\">2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\" selected>3</option>\n        </select>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"../_images/background2.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#efefef\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#efefef\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        \n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"title col-12 pb-5 align-center\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n                <h2 class=\"pb-3 mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">\n                    Наши специалисты</span></h2>\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n                    Fusce ornare risus vel tellus tempor tempor. Suspendisse ut lobortis sem, aliquam consequat nisi.\n                </h3>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"mbr-testimonial align-center col-12 col-md-6 md-pb\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-4': TestimonialsCount > 2 }\">\n                <div class=\"panel-item\">\n                    <div class=\"card-block\">\n                        <div class=\"testimonial-photo\" mbr-if=\"showImages\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/director1-754x1131.jpg\" alt>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-footer\">\n                            <h3 class=\"mbr-author-name pb-4 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showName\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-name\" mbr-text>Ковалевский Максим Борисович</h3>\n                            <h4 class=\"mbr-author-desc pb-1 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showBio\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-desc\" mbr-text>\n                                Директор<br><br>Врач-стоматолог-ортопед высшей квалификационной категории</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"phone pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showphone\" data-app-selector=\".phone\" mbr-text>0704 - 94 25 49&nbsp;</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"mail pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showmail\" data-app-selector=\".mail\" mbr-text>\n                                sara@bosumhus.se\n                            </h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce ornare risus vel tellus\n                            tempor tempor. Suspendisse ut lobortis sem, aliquam consequat nisi. Praesent ac scelerisque\n                            nulla. Maecenas sed magna quis leo fringilla molestie.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-testimonial align-center col-12 col-md-6 md-pb\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-4': TestimonialsCount > 2 }\" mbr-if=\"TestimonialsCount>1\">\n                <div class=\"panel-item\">\n                    <div class=\"card-block\">\n                        <div class=\"testimonial-photo\" mbr-if=\"showImages\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/2-754x1121.jpg\" alt>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-footer\">\n                            <h3 class=\"mbr-author-name pb-4 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showName\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-name\" mbr-text>Ковалевская Виктория Вячеславовна</h3>\n                            <h4 class=\"mbr-author-desc pb-1 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showBio\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-desc\" mbr-text>Врач-стоматолог-ортопед 2 квалификационной категории</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"phone pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showphone\" data-app-selector=\".phone\" mbr-text>0704 - 94 25 49&nbsp;</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"mail pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showmail\" data-app-selector=\".mail\" mbr-text>\n                                sara@bosumhus.se\n                            </h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce ornare risus vel tellus\n                            tempor tempor. Suspendisse ut lobortis sem, aliquam consequat nisi. Praesent ac scelerisque\n                            nulla. Maecenas sed magna quis leo fringilla molestie.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-testimonial align-center col-12 col-md-6 md-pb\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-4': TestimonialsCount > 2 }\" mbr-if=\"TestimonialsCount>2\">\n                <div class=\"panel-item\">\n                    <div class=\"card-block\">\n                        <div class=\"testimonial-photo\" mbr-if=\"showImages\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/3-1-654x981.jpg\" alt>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-footer\">\n                            <h3 class=\"mbr-author-name pb-4 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showName\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-name\" mbr-text>Юрченко Алла Сергеевна</h3>\n                            <h4 class=\"mbr-author-desc pb-1 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showBio\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-desc\" mbr-text>Врач-стоматолог-ортодонт 2 квалификационной категории</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"phone pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showphone\" data-app-selector=\".phone\" mbr-text>0704 - 94 25 49&nbsp;</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"mail pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showmail\" data-app-selector=\".mail\" mbr-text>\n                                sara@bosumhus.se\n                            </h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce ornare risus vel tellus\n                            tempor tempor. Suspendisse ut lobortis sem, aliquam consequat nisi. Praesent ac scelerisque\n                            nulla. Maecenas sed magna quis leo fringilla molestie.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
