thor-name pb-4 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showName\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-name\" mbr-text>Машинян Роман Хачатурович</h3>\n                            <h4 class=\"mbr-author-desc pb-1 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showBio\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-desc\" mbr-text>Врач-стоматолог-хирург 1 квалификационной категории</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"phone pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showphone\" data-app-selector=\".phone\" mbr-text>0704 - 94 25 49&nbsp;</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"mail pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showmail\" data-app-selector=\".mail\" mbr-text>\n                                sara@bosumhus.se\n                            </h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce ornare risus vel tellus\n                            tempor tempor. Suspendisse ut lobortis sem, aliquam consequat nisi. Praesent ac scelerisque\n                            nulla. Maecenas sed magna quis leo fringilla molestie.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-testimonial align-center col-12 col-md-6 md-pb\" mbr-class=\"{'col-lg-4': TestimonialsCount > 2 }\" mbr-if=\"TestimonialsCount>2\">\n                <div class=\"panel-item\">\n                    <div class=\"card-block\">\n                        <div class=\"testimonial-photo\" mbr-if=\"showImages\">\n                            <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/6-831x1247.jpg\" alt>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"card-footer\">\n                            <h3 class=\"mbr-author-name pb-4 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showName\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-name\" mbr-text>Буева Вера Сергеевна</h3>\n                            <h4 class=\"mbr-author-desc pb-1 mbr-black mbr-bold mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showBio\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-author-desc\" mbr-text>Врач-стоматолог-терапевт 1 квалификационной категории</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"phone pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showphone\" data-app-selector=\".phone\" mbr-text>0704 - 94 25 49&nbsp;</h4>\n                            <h4 class=\"mail pb-1 mbr-black mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showmail\" data-app-selector=\".mail\" mbr-text>\n                                sara@bosumhus.se\n                            </h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce ornare risus vel tellus\n                            tempor tempor. Suspendisse ut lobortis sem, aliquam consequat nisi. Praesent ac scelerisque\n                            nulla. Maecenas sed magna quis leo fringilla molestie.</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
